<p><center><h2>Hamas: A Behavioral Profile</h2></center>
<P><b>Shaul Mishal and Avraham Sela</b>
<BR><b></b>
<P><font size="-1">Tel Aviv University
<BR>The Tami Steinmetz Center for Peace Research
<BR><FONT SIZE="-1">Copyright (1997) The Tami Steinmetz Center for Peace Research Tel Aviv
University, Tel-Aviv 69978, Israel.</FONT></font>

